{
  "arquivo": "ca04_mv3_02",
  "total": 79,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What are you guys doing?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ah, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Look, Uesugi-san.\\nThere are so many Okinawan sweets lined up!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Didn't we just eat breakfast?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Well, I couldn't resist the delicious smell!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're not Itsuki.\\nBut, it does smell really good.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Those are 'sata andagi...'\\nWow, they even have \\n'black sugar caneles.'",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "You can buy them one at a time,\\nso let's try one.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Then let's go with sata andagi.\\nIt's like a donut, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "That's right.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Sata is sugar! Anda is oil! Agi is frying!\\nCombine them all! Sata andagi!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What's with that local superhero-esque catchphrase.\\nYet, Yotsuba, you sure know a lot.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Hehehe.\\nI did my research on things everyone would like\\nbefore we went on the trip.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "If only you could use that passion for studying,\\nyou wouldn't have had so much trouble with exams.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Y-you're not supposed to say that.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "What? Miku?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's nothing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But, there are so many types.\\nNot just plain ones, but also black sugar,\\npurple sweet potato, pineapple, and mango flavors.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here, plain is the way to go.\\nI want to try the basic flavor in its original place.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's still a bit hot.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's freshly fried, huh.\\nSounding more and more delicious by the second.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah.\\nBut this is bigger than I thought.\\nI might not be able to finish it.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Then, why don't we split it in half?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Oh, right.\\nLet's split it in half, then...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here you go, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh? Whaaa?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Should I eat this?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'm still a little full.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "It's only half. It's fine.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, what are you saying that based on?\\nI don't have a stomach like Itsuki.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Should I tell Itsuki what you just said?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Please don't...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I want to split it fifty-fifty with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here, I'll feed you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Futaro.\\nOpen wide.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oily food, in the morning?\\nThat may not be the best idea.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Haha, what?\\nYou're like an old grandpa.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But we ate a gentle rice porridge for breakfast.\\nEating such an oily food here,\\nwould make all that go to waste wouldn't it...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "But if you don't eat it,\\nit would be a waste of what I bought.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Well, that IS true.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Grandpa Futaro.\\nDo your best and eat up.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "*sigh*\\nWhy do you want me to eat it that much?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I want to split it fifty-fifty with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here, I'll feed you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Futaro.\\nOpen wide.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "How about you split it in half with Yotsuba instead?\\nHonestly, that's what I thought you were gonna do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, that's what you were thinking, right?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ahaha...\\nYeah, that was the plan.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "That's just a misunderstanding between the two of you.\\nI intended to split it with you from the beginning.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "So here you go, Futaro.\\nThis is for you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Sorry, but I'm still full.\\nYou should share it with Yotsuba.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I want to split it fifty-fifty with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Here, I'll feed you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Come on, Futaro.\\nOpen wide.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "H-hey, what are you doing...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Uwaaaaa...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ahhhhhh.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Even though Yotsuba is here,\\n what is Miku thinking...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "NOM!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "AH!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Nom, nom...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Why did you eat it, Yotsuba?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Sorry Miku, it just looked so good.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "I'll buy another one as an apology!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "W-wait, Yotsuba,\\nShe only cut it in half\\nbecause I couldn't eat the whole thing.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Ah, that's right!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yotsuba, do you want more?\\nCome to think of it, I'm not that hungry.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "Is that so?\\nAlright, I'll have the sata andagi,\\nso for you, maybe something lighter?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Sure. Thanks.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "How about ice cream?\\nMiku, you like soft serve matcha ice cream,\\nbut that's not very Okinawan, is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Something not too sweet would be good, I think.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(What's going on with Miku?\\n And Yotsuba earlier, as well...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}